quran[7{c,v,t}:
3,71,ae ahal kitaab! kyun haq ko baatil ka rang charha kar mushtaba banatay ho? kyun jantay bojhtayhaq ko chupatay ho ?
3,72,"ahal kitaab mein se aik giroh kehta hai ke is nabi ke maan-ne walon par jo kuch nazil howa hai is par subah imaan lao aur shaam ko is se inkaar kar do, shayad is tarkeeb se yeh log apne imaan se phir jayen"
3,73,"neez yeh log aapas mein kehte hain ke apne mazhab walay ke siwa kisi ki baat nah manu ae Nabi ! un se keh do ke,"" asal mein hadaayat to Allah ki hadaayat hai aur yeh usi ki deen hai ke kisi ko wohi kuch day diya jaye jo kabhi tum ko diya gaya tha, ya yeh ke dosaron ko tumahray Rab ke huzoor paish karne ke liye tumahray khilaaf quwwat Hujjat mil jaye"" ae Nabi ! un se kaho ke,"" fazl o Sharf Allah ke ikhtiyar mein hai, jisay chahay ataa farmaiye woh wasee al nazr hai aur sab kuch jaanta hai"
3,74,"apni rehmat ke liye jis ko chahta hai makhsoos kar laita hai aur is ka fazl bohat bara hai """
3,75,"ahal kitaab mein koi to aisa hai ke agar tum is ke aetmaad par maal o doulat ka aik dhair bhi day do to woh tumhara maal tumhe ada kar day ga, aur kisi ka haal yeh hai ke agar tum aik dinar ke maamla mein bhi is par bharosa karo to woh ada nah kere ga ila yeh ke tum is ke sir par sawaar ho jao unn ki is ikhlaqi haalat ka sabab yeh hai ke woh kehte hain,"" ummyu-N ( ghair yahodi logon ) ke maamla mein hum par koi muwakhza nahi hai"" aur yeh baat woh mehez jhoot ghurr kar Allah ki taraf mansoob karte hain, halaank inhen maloom hai ke Allah ne aisi koi baat nahi farmai hai aakhir kyun unn se baz purse nah hogi ?"
3,76,"jo bhi apne ehad ko poora kere ga aur buraiee se bach kar rahay ga woh Allah ka mehboob banay ga, kyunkay parhaiz gaar log Allah ko pasand hain"
3,77,"rahay woh log jo Allah ke ehad aur apni qasmon ko thori qeemat par beech daaltay hain, to un ke liye akhirat mein koi hissa nahi, Allah qayamat ke roz nah unn se baat kere ga nah unn ki taraf dekhe ga aur nah inhen pak kere ga, balkay unn ke liye to sakht dard naak saza hai"
